The paper deals with anomaly detection in network traffic, which is a topic closely related to computer networks and network security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of complex network models and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to several other categories such as cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
